rael-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-settlers-have-found-a-new-way-to-abuse-palestinian-shepherds-bankrupting-them/0000018d-4822-dc44-a5bf-c8b681660000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列历史上最伟大的恐吓者”：内塔尼亚胡的恐吓策略如何操纵以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-one-generates-fear-like-him-how-netanyahus-scare-tactics-manipulate-israelis/0000018d-47c8-d02c-a79f-47db0d710000</link><description>乌里尔·阿布洛夫说，内塔尼亚胡权力的秘密在于滥用权力。作为恐惧政治的研究者，他试图理解我们如何才能爬出深渊，回到希望政治</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 23:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-one-generates-fear-like-him-how-netanyahus-scare-tactics-manipulate-israelis/0000018d-47c8-d02c-a79f-47db0d710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称，他们被俘的儿子被哈马斯杀害。然后病理学家出现了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-their-captive-son-was-killed-by-hamas-then-a-pathologist-showed-up/0000018d-4756-d35c-a39f-ef5e4de10000</link><description>她的儿子被哈马斯扣为人质并在加沙被发现死亡，而对他尸体的尸检和有关他死亡的军方报告都没有结论，愤怒的马扬·谢尔曼要求以色列国防军和国家给出答案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-their-captive-son-was-killed-by-hamas-then-a-pathologist-showed-up/0000018d-4756-d35c-a39f-ef5e4de10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的人道主义灾难是国际法院对以色列种族灭绝裁决的核心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/gazan-humanitarian-crisis-overshadows-everything-else-in-icjs-preliminary-genocide-ruling/0000018d-4739-d02c-a79f-47bb34a90000</link><description>国际法院的临时裁决重点关注加沙最紧迫的问题：巴勒斯坦人的灾难性状况，以及释放以色列人质的必要性</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/gazan-humanitarian-crisis-overshadows-everything-else-in-icjs-preliminary-genocide-ruling/0000018d-4739-d02c-a79f-47bb34a90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队任命周四在加沙地带战斗中丧生的以色列国防军预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/israeli-army-names-idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-thursday/0000018d-4790-d35c-a39f-efda5d230000</link><description>中士。埃利兰·耶格尔 (Eliran Yeger) 少校，36 岁，来自特拉维夫，在加沙地带南部的战斗中身亡。 “埃利兰确实是一位伟大的父亲，他正在努力成为一名更好的父亲。我觉得这是最大的悲伤，”他的遗孀在接受采访时说道</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:14:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/israeli-army-names-idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-thursday/0000018d-4790-d35c-a39f-efda5d230000</guid></item><item><title>当地档案馆偶然发现了德国犹太人被驱逐的秘密拍摄照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/secretly-captured-images-of-german-jews-expulsion-found-by-chance-in-local-archive/0000018d-425b-dc44-a5bf-caff994d0000</link><description>这些照片是由一位犹太业余摄影师冒着生命危险秘密拍摄的，展示了德国布雷斯劳市犹太人被驱逐的情景，这些照片在国际大屠杀纪念日之前首次曝光</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 20:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/secretly-captured-images-of-german-jews-expulsion-found-by-chance-in-local-archive/0000018d-425b-dc44-a5bf-caff994d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯播出三名以色列人质在加沙被囚禁的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-three-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-captivity/0000018d-473c-d02c-a79f-47bf122b0000</link><description>在视频中，30 岁的兽医护士 Doron Steinbrecher 和 19 岁的以色列国防军士兵 Daniela Gilboa 和 Karina Ariav 表示，他们已被囚禁 107 天</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 19:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-three-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-captivity/0000018d-473c-d02c-a79f-47bf122b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谴责国际法院考虑种族灭绝；沙特称以色列“违反”联合国规则，美国称其“毫无根据”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-icj-genocide-mull-u-s-labels-it-unfounded-saudis-note-violations/0000018d-46e2-d35c-a39f-eefaac3f0000</link><description>以色列政治领导人一致谴责法院考虑种族灭绝指控，而巴勒斯坦总理则宣称，“以色列逃避惩罚的日子已经结束了”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 18:57:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-decries-icj-genocide-mull-u-s-labels-it-unfounded-saudis-note-violations/0000018d-46e2-d35c-a39f-eefaac3f0000</guid></item><item><title>2014年，内塔尼亚胡就哈马斯屠杀阴谋发出预警。九年后，10 月 7 日发生了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-netanyahu-forewarned-of-a-hamas-massacre-plot-nine-years-later-oct-7-happened/0000018d-4591-d02c-a79f-479bf39c0000</link><description>2014年加沙行动前不久，以色列领导人获悉以色列南部计划进行大屠杀，并绑架士兵和平民作为讨价还价的筹码。一名以色列国防军将军当时告诉他的同事，“我不想在周六早上报告五个基布兹已被占领”</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:57:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-netanyahu-forewarned-of-a-hamas-massacre-plot-nine-years-later-oct-7-happened/0000018d-4591-d02c-a79f-479bf39c0000</guid></item><item><title>优先考虑人质的以色列人是真正理性的声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院在国际法院就种族灭绝案向以色列发出警告。这就是内塔尼亚胡应该担心的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/icj-fires-israel-a-warning-shot-over-genocide-case-this-is-why-netanyahu-should-worry/0000018d-4625-dc44-a5bf-ceb7d5cf0000</link><description>国际法院周五的临时裁决给以色列带来了好坏参半的消息：尽管以色列没有被告知在加沙停火，但其命令可能会给以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和他的极右翼部长带来严重的头痛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 15:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/icj-fires-israel-a-warning-shot-over-genocide-case-this-is-why-netanyahu-should-worry/0000018d-4625-dc44-a5bf-ceb7d5cf0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院裁定以色列必须避免在加沙实施种族灭绝行为，不得下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/icj-rules-israel-must-avoid-genocidal-acts-in-gaza-stops-short-of-ordering-cease-fire/0000018d-4606-d35c-a39f-ee5e5b7e0000</link><description>尽管此案的最终裁决可能需要数年时间，但以色列必须履行法院下令的六项临时措施，以保护加沙的巴勒斯坦人，包括提供援助和惩罚煽动种族灭绝的行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 15:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/icj-rules-israel-must-avoid-genocidal-acts-in-gaza-stops-short-of-ordering-cease-fire/0000018d-4606-d35c-a39f-ee5e5b7e0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院裁定以色列必须“采取一切措施”避免在加沙发生种族灭绝行为、煽动行为，但不下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/top-un-court-hands-down-preliminary-ruling-in-south-africa-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-451e-dc44-a5bf-cdbeb41c0000</link><description>国际法院初步裁决没有下令停止加沙战争，称以色列必须采取一切措施保护平民，惩罚煽动行为。内塔尼亚胡：法院维护以色列自卫权是正确的，但不应该辩论种族灭绝指控</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 10:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/top-un-court-hands-down-preliminary-ruling-in-south-africa-genocide-case-against-israel/0000018d-451e-dc44-a5bf-cdbeb41c0000</guid></item><item><title>从否认大屠杀到所有人的大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/from-holocaust-denial-to-everyone-gets-their-own-revisionism-and-relativism-after-oct-7/0000018d-44be-d02c-a79f-47bfbbf80000</link><description>大屠杀的去犹太化和普遍化不可避免地意味着它后来将成为殴打犹太人自己的一根棍子。那些将 10 月 7 日描述为“另一场大屠杀”的人并不好得多</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 09:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/from-holocaust-denial-to-everyone-gets-their-own-revisionism-and-relativism-after-oct-7/0000018d-44be-d02c-a79f-47bfbbf80000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列建立渠道寻求加沙战争平民死亡问题的答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/u-s-establishes-channel-with-israel-to-seek-answers-on-civilian-deaths-in-gaza-war/0000018d-44a1-dc44-a5bf-ccb744f50000</link><description>据哈马斯卫生部称，以色列针对哈马斯的行动造成了巨大伤亡，拜登政府面临越来越大的压力，此次行动已造成超过 25,000 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 08:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/u-s-establishes-channel-with-israel-to-seek-answers-on-civilian-deaths-in-gaza-war/0000018d-44a1-dc44-a5bf-ccb744f50000</guid></item><item><title>随着内塔尼亚胡的失败不断累积，以色列总理的信用丧失带来了更大的危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahus-failings-pile-up-israels-out-of-credit-pm-poses-even-greater-danger/0000018d-4252-d02c-a79f-43db08760000</link><description>从人质危机到哈马斯垮台，现在是时候说出众所周知的事情了：内塔尼亚胡不可能获胜。与此同时，塔利·戈特利夫（Tally Gotliv）是他的政党在议会中最新的破坏者</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 04:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahus-failings-pile-up-israels-out-of-credit-pm-poses-even-greater-danger/0000018d-4252-d02c-a79f-43db08760000</guid></item><item><title>退伍前夕，以色列士兵谈论战斗、人质以及他们进入加沙的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-discharge-israeli-soldiers-talk-combat-hostages-and-why-they-went-into-gaza/0000018d-421a-dc44-a5bf-cabedf330000</link><description>戈拉尼旅士兵获得了为期一周的休假，在此期间他们讨论了在加沙的三个月不间断的战斗。 与此同时，以色列军方发起了一场针对国家审计长的运动，后者希望调查以色列国防军对 10 月 7 日及之后的处理方式</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-discharge-israeli-soldiers-talk-combat-hostages-and-why-they-went-into-gaza/0000018d-421a-dc44-a5bf-cabedf330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标，据报道两人死亡；火箭弹袭击以色列北部边境城镇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/report-u-s-sets-up-channel-with-israel-seeking-answers-on-civilian-casualties/0000018d-43b5-dc44-a5bf-cbb79fb40000</link><description>美国因涉嫌参与 10 月 7 日袭击的员工而暂停向近东救济工程处提供资金 ■ 人质家属试图在凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点阻止人道主义援助进入加沙 ■ 资料来源：以色列、哈马斯就人质交易的大部分问题达成基本谅解 ■ 哈马斯加沙卫生部报告称，加沙死亡人数已超过 26,000 人</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 03:13:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-live/report-u-s-sets-up-channel-with-israel-seeking-answers-on-civilian-casualties/0000018d-43b5-dc44-a5bf-cbb79fb40000</guid></item></channel></rss>